title: List of Jordanian detainees at Guantanamo Bay
data: Khalid Mahomoud Abdul Wahab Al Asmr
section_text: The United States Department of Defense acknowledges holding eight Jordanian captives in Guantanamo . [ 1 ] A total of 778 captives have been held in extrajudicial detention in the Guantanamo Bay detention camps , in Cuba since the camps opened on January 11 , 2002 The camp population peaked in 2004 at approximately 660 . Only nineteen new captives , all `` high value detainees '' have been transferred there since the United States Supreme Court 's ruling in Rasul v. Bush . As of July 2012 the camp population was at approximately 170 . This number had dropped to 40 by May of 2018 .
